# Day 03 - Password Strength Analyzer

A simple Python-based tool that analyzes password strength using basic security rules and complexity checks.

---

## Features

- Password length analysis
- Uppercase and lowercase checks
- Number detection
- Special character detection
- Simple password strength rating

---

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Regular Expressions

---

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/viehgroup/cybersecurity-automation.git
cd Day-03-Password-Strength-Analyzer
```

---

## Usage

```bash
python password_checker.py
```

Enter a password when prompted.

---

## Example Output

```text
Enter Password: Test@123

Password Strength: STRONG

Checks Passed:
[+] Minimum length verified
[+] Uppercase letter detected
[+] Lowercase letter detected
[+] Number detected
[+] Special character detected
```

